Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:52.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}They're seven deadly sins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You feel alive when you step inside
