Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}人たらしめる罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:06.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}それはいつだって付き纏うんだ Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}死に至る罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}犯しても次へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}目を逸らさずに Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ただ前へ前へ Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I gotta make it make it again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:13.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}増していく代償
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:14.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}向かう先が地獄だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:17.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}後悔なんてない Anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:20.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Fallin' fallin' down 暗闇へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But, never going back 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狼煙高く上げて Now dive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}煩悩なんてモノ Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}性懲りも無く Fight 仲間と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I won't run away from my sin no more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何処までも抗って Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:39.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 超えていく 恐れずに Bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not afraid, bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:44.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if I'm drown in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分のチカラに変え Wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 捻じ曲げる System
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never ever follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:58.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 立ち向かう and I'll defeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:46.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像人性一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你将凝视深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:52.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你踏入其中 你会发觉自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:57.32,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}踏入未知领域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:02:00.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那些漂亮话 早就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.51,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人得以为人的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:06.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总是伴随着我们 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.52,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}致命的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.15,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不要转移视线 赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.55,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只是向前 向前 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.18,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须再次取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:13.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}代价在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:14.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使前方是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:17.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不再有任何后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:20.63,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坠落 坠落 堕入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.18,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是 永远不回头 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.15,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}高举烽烟 然后潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.36,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与烦恼说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惩前毖后 与伙伴一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.00,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}活着就是为了择日赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.68,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再逃避我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我将一直抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:39.68,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 无畏地超越 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不害怕 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:44.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使我将陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要将其转化为我的力量 消除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.67,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 扭曲这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.31,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:58.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 我将面对挑战并战胜自己
